CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 12, 1951, pg. 25, reads: "Provident's Leading Agents - Some of the leaders in Provident Home Life Insurance Company's 1951 production, collection and increase championship competitions in the Pittsburgh district are shown here. Left to right, standing: James Mason, J.W. Willis and Alonza E. Palm. Sitting: Agnes Wormsley and Nannie Forrester - Photo by Jean, Harris Studio"
TitMainTitle: Agnes Wormsley and Nannie Forrester in front, and James Mason, J. W. Willis, and Alonza E. Palm, standing in front of nativity tapestry, in interior with wooden chairs
